graph TD
    RawLidar[Raw LiDAR measurement] -->|TFmini serial parser| LidarProc[LidarProcessor class]
    LidarProc -->|Distance values| Kalman[RangeKalmanFilter class]
    
    RawCam[Raw Camera frame] -->|YOLO ONNX model| ONNX[YOLOv11 Inference]
    ONNX -->|Detect coordinates| CamDet[CameraObstacleDetector class]
    
    Kalman -->|Filtered range metres| Fusion[SensorFusionNode class]
    CamDet -->|Obstacle bounding boxes| Fusion
    
    Fusion -->|Fused threat coordinate block| Predictor[TrajectoryPredictor class]
    Predictor -->|Calculate TTC| Decision[Dynamic Steering/Yaw Override]
